The paper proposes a modification to Capsule Networks, a type of neural network architecture, to improve the routing procedure. This involves optimizing coupling coefficients in the routing procedure, which is a task typically associated with neural network optimization and training. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
